{
  "stem": "20035.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There is just-- we had-- we had to go and pump up water from a-- from a well.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was-- for the first time, you felt like a third-class citizen who really doesn't belong.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Dehumanizing it as much as possible.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The food basically came in on a pushcart from the front door, from the front gate.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, military handed over the-- well, the-- these pushcarts to kids, like my brother and I, or the younger generation, who were stronger.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And basically, we had to bring it to different barracks and different-- not even barracks, buildings.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] --that was the distribution.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was-- it was-- it was not superbly organized.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jews in Hungary were not organized the same way as we call it here.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like I mentioned it, you mean, my-- my grandfather was the President of the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father was the President the school board.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they tried to comfort our group.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But there wasn't a general major group who-- who even had the right-- first of all, nobody had any idea.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The shock was tremendous.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody, really, idea what hit us, what's really happening.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Once again, there was no question that we are going to go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The younger, able people, they are going to go and work in labor camps.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Work maybe as digging trenches, maybe go all the way up to the front.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But these were rumors.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody had an idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a shock.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Shamefully, I have to say it, in 1944, this was already 1944, end of May.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We never heard of, we never knew that there is such a thing as a concentration camp, as an extermination camp, where Jews are being destroyed by-- Jews are being killed.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We lived in a bubble.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
